Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My child, heed my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story I'm about to tell\Nis a very important one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I begin now the story of\Na long, long journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will be passed on from\Nparent to child without end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk too slow. Hurry up, will you?\NThat's all you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.43,0:00:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk too slow. Hurry up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.67,0:00:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You walk too slow. Hurry up, will you?\NHey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.37,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what a ramen set is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely starving right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I desperately want to eat a ramen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'm broke. And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. It's time for a fun puppet show.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you to pay me before you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.30,0:01:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? Isn't it great?\NIsn't it interesting? Isn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this filthy doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ugly-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.74,0:01:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't he do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that! And that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honest kids are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can pay me as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm honestly saying it's ugly-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.62,0:01:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should we pay money for\Nsomething like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We watched the vapor trails
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.11,0:02:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As they disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran from the blinding light
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In vexation we let go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still places she cannot reach
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She gazes with wistful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children walk along the tracks in summer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In both hands, their wish to take wing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We chased and chased vanishing vapor trails
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:03:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day we climbed over that hill
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfailingly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just like we have always
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stood straight and tall
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will stay as strong as the god of the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-a ramen set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is she after? Money?\NI have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and buy something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had a little trouble there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Thick\NPEACH NECTAR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Thick\NPEACH NECTAR\NExtra Thick Peach Nectar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Thick Peach Nectar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.13,0:05:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to make a fool of me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is delicious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, the kids were playing on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking it looked fun,\Nand I wanted to play too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to you as you slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.47,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been sleeping there since yesterday,\Nhaven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I poked at you to wake you up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't look like you were going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so hungry I couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work? What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A puppet sho...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, isn't it? That's enough. Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!\NIt's hot, isn't it? That's enough. Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crow! Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going after that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was. I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can play with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been hanging around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been hanging around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been hanging around me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I want to play on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go running, or splash water at each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, we'll say "See you tomorrow!"\NAnd go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that like being friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know each other's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Misuzu Kamio. Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But listen! I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, so I have to earn some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up following her home,\Nlured by the thought of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to eat with someone else, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you usually eat alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom gets home late. And I don't have a dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish eating, let's go play, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.08,0:07:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. If it gets late, I'll have trouble\Nfinding a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a place to stay yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll probably be sleeping under the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, listen up. We just met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!\NAnd you have no idea who the heck I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you have no idea who the heck I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!\NWho in their right mind would put\Nsomeone like that up for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in their right mind would put\Nsomeone like that up for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother probably wouldn't allow it\Nin the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's really lax, so I don't\Nthink there will be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I shouldn't be talking about\Nmy own mother like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, it's okay for you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired. I don't have the energy\Nto play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can play tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer vacation, so I have lots of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say... What kind of use do you think math is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think quadratic functions\Nwill be useful in my future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing helping you\Nwith your homework, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, your eyes are too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito, you sound just like my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran into the shed with her motorcycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really sure it's okay for me to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I'll smooth it over with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can let a young guy\Nlike this stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.18,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell ya\Nto stop saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are ya to Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CLASS-\NMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... her classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Yer kinda old, aren't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DON'T FALL\NFOR ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I would?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you do seem to have pluck.\NI like that about ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yukito is a really nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. He can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serious? Why, I'm dead serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are TWO conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TABI\NGARASV\NSAKE\NAnd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TABI\NGARASV\NSAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TABI\NGARASV\NSAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be my drinking partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be my drinking partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then in the end, this is what the guy said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I guess maybe I was the one who fell in love."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaddya think? Do I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The fish you let escape\Nwas a mermaid, you know..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was that? Pretty good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's in top form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Freeloader. Why're ya looking so glum?\NWhy don't ya join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MY EYES!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything'll do. An erotic confession\Nor a hidden talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.16,0:10:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I earn my living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother used to travel with this as her trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do we get to the punchline?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. You've no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing.\NThere's no gimmick behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the strings show,\Nit's better if it's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's going off to the shed on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with having no talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink up and forget about it, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Haruko. Haruko Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me another one, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you my name so ya\Nwouldn't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so thoughtless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... You a runaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are ya following a goal or a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, compared to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a funny guy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I have a pretty good eye\Nwhen it comes to men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind if you stayed on for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something a little unsure about her,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's careless, and once something catches\Nher eye, she goes off like a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, a babysitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like you to correct those\Nfunny things she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard her say "gao," haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's frustrated or about to cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's supposed to sound like a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves dinosaurs. She's been saying\Nthat since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still just a child...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Isn't it summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to take remedial classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Haruko already left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She leaves early every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I've had\Ncompany for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing today, Yukito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll walk you to school.\NHaruko asked me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said to watch that you don't\Ndo anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't trust me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done! A map of this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will tell you where you\Ncan find people gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should help with your work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, I'm in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come for you after school. We'll meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese use\Nthese, right?\NHere\NI'm\Nstudying.\NMunch\NIts the ocean! Munch Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese use\Nthese, right?\NHere\NI'm\Nstudying.\NMunch\NIt's the ocean! Munch Delicious!\NW-what in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-what in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this how she sees the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you this town's local legendary being?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, if I do it a favor,\Nlike in those fairytales,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe it'll give me something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Come here. I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.69,0:14:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it such a wonderful act it makes you\Nfeel like giving me something in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PIKO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!\NHold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!\NPiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.34,0:14:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up, you evil space being.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko... Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:14:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange extraterrestrial\Nran away with my puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Potato isn't an extraterrestrial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a neighborhood stray dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, that's really a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko! Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko! Pikopikopiko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry he caused you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Potato said that he brought\Nyour puppet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he wanted to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.31,0:15:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!\NIt seems he wanted to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you can understand what he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We're best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are worlds\NI know nothing about here on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope! I have to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kano Kirishima. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukito Kunisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have some free time, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then you will be Citizen Number 2\Nof Planet Dilly-Dally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Number 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! And Potato is Number 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do the citizens of Planet Dilly-Dally do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just have time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the fate of those from Planet Dilly-Dally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? We have nothing to do, do we, Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to school now.\NSo I'll say good-bye for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were from Planet Dilly-Dally?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believed that? Such a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all the girls in that uniform weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever wished you could do magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stunned! So long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did your work go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a mint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find someplace where there are more\Npeople or I won't be able to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this place so quiet when people\Nshould be traveling to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this station has been closed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told me that earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko told me to scold you when you said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miss Tohno...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. Quite a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm astonished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.91,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting some sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. It's evening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who the heck is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minagi Tohno. She's my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's smart. She's at the top of our grade,\Nand she's president of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please just call me Tohno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukito is flying like a leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Let's hurry up and\Ngo back to blowing bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you know, I'm doing really good now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not. I'm Michiru, Minagi's best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miss Tohno's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you another one of\NMinagi's classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an innocent passerby who got\Nbowled over by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it! Minagi, this is\Na perverted kidnapper who's after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm in this group too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's are you calling a kidnapper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! He's agitated.\NWe young girls are in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, did you hear that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kamio, who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki. He's a traveler\Nwho's staying with us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A homeless, perverted kidnapper?\NHe's a lost cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kamio, I think we'd better be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I was doing really well\Nblowing bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it some more.\NKami-Kami can join us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-Kami? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting dark, so let's do it again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pack a lunch for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Kamio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito Kunisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.41,0:20:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, Will you make me\Na hamburger tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something wrong to that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up not making a single yen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were standing there like that\Nwhen we met yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was little,\NI've had this longing for the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have this feeling like...\Nthere's another me there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a romantic thought?\NThat the real you is in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must feel really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could see far into the distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything on the ground\Nwould look so insignificant...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd probably feel very gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the start of a summer that, for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seemed as short as the twinkling of a star,\Nand as long as all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching hold of the remnant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of a dream that fades to white
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The young boy runs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.51,0:22:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he lets go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It vanishes forever with
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cry of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gentleness, once so apparent, is now gone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:23:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes remain on the steps my feet take
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing forever the sounds of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That had faded away by morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always following in the footsteps we left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always following in the footsteps we left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.31,0:23:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.41,0:23:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode\NIt might be the other you\Nthat I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be the other you\Nthat I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.85,0:23:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cut out to be a parent.\NI should have stayed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream. A strange dream about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:23:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a world I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything went on into infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Did you have wings in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2\NListen. Did you have wings in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2